 Delta State Governor Ifeanyi Okowa has arrived at the Peoples Democratic Party (PDP) secretariat for his screening, as the running mate to Atiku Abubakar, the party’s presidential candidate. This is as Atiku is said to have finally settled for Okowa, dropping the Rivers State Governor, Nyesom Wike, who was earlier recommended by the party’s selection committee. Read also: Running mate: Disregard misrepresenting report on Wike – PDP Details later